headline: Cloudflare Stock Gains 15% as Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: NET shares soar after Q4 earnings and revenues surpass estimates, with the company initiating strong guidance for the first quarter and full-year 2026.

headline: Leadership Shift And Robust 2025 Results Could Be A Game Changer For Amphenol (APH)
summary: In late January 2026, Amphenol reported full-year 2025 results showing US$23.09 billion in sales and US$4.27 billion in net income, issued first-quarter 2026 sales guidance of US$6.90–US$7.00 billion, continued share repurchases, and in early February affirmed a US$0.25 per share first-quarter 2026 dividend.
